		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Very weird thread..
<br />
<br />Who else but Nintendo would design SMB3?
<br />
<br />Metal Slug was designed by Nazca, former Irem employees. 
<br />
<br />If you like Metal Slug's art then play: 
<br />
<br />Air Duel
<br />Armed Police Unit Gallop
<br />Undercover Cops
<br />In the Hunt
<br />(Last Resort)
<br />
<br />GunForce and Geostorm are basically Metal Slug prototypes with good art, bad gameplay in my opinion.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
